<note>The shape of 
<foreign>ccha</foreign> is extremely eccentric. It seems that the scribe first engraved 
<foreign>cha</foreign> on the line and then added 
<foreign>c</foreign> on top of it as an afterthought and with a shape that is easily confused as a vowel marker 
<foreign>i</foreign>.</note>
                 </app>
                 
